Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:04.02,Narration Off,,2,2,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a penetratingly precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he's on a roll, there's no stopping him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:09.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's a special — Conan's first case back when he was Shin'ichi.{literal: 'Conan's first Shin'ichi-era case'}
