Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:57.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tōkyō International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plane we're gonna be riding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Boeing 747.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a jumbo jet, 70.7 metres long!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorō Mouri, private eye, babysitting brats on a trip to Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure have some nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who went all 'Wait for me, my cute seaside angels' last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was before I knew I had to babysit a bunch of brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason we're even here is because\NDr Agasa won this trip on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful that you can come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how come I can't see our lucky doctor yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doc's not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just called him. He told me he came\Ndown with a cold and can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though he asked for lots of souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's going to pass as well\Nto look after the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's buy her a lot of souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, the houses keep getting smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was up all night reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just remembering the flight I took last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, Shin'ichi also fell\Nasleep right after we took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and that detective kid ran off to LA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I was away on a trip that I won at the neighbourhood drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just went to visit his parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, teenage kids don't go on {\i1}overseas{\i0} trips together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, his parents were the ones who sent me the ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, back then, he didn't try anything... {\i1}funny{\i0}, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by 'funny'?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How do I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sit down, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya talkin' to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you put out that cigarette?\NThis is a non-smoking section.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.25,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tsuneo Ukai (47)\NExecutive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,You're causing trouble\Nfor the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,If you want to smoke,\Nthere's an area in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.54,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro Ōtaka (29)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll try to be more {\i1}thoughtful{\i0} next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.38,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi Amano (27)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.43,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please knock it off, Kazuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are ya seriously scolding your boyfriend who's gonna be stinkin' rich soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lighten up some!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That American newspaper said they'll give me a whole lotta green for these negatives, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} those negatives are the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:53.49,Dialogue Top,,2,2,0,,I don't know if those actually are scandalous shots of a powerful American senator or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,Chizuru Tachikawa (29)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you've got the wrong man,\Nthis'll just be a bad joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already faxed 'em two of the shots to confirm it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine and all, but just don't\Nforget that we're on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This deal with your shots comes second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait 'til ya get a load of our surfing skills.{it's 'our' skills, cuz of the 'ore-tachi' here, right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Saginuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:23.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Noboru Saginuma (30)\NPhotographer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's with him? He's already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, guess I'll catch a nap too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,Edward Crowe (51)\NFreelance Journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I help you, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling airsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any airsickness pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir. May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm not too fond of planes.\NI just feel uncomfortable sitting still.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Could you do me a little favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sick. The stewardess went to get me some medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you take the airsick pills I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd. They seem to be\Nworking fine on Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to switch seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sitting by the window might make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's the one who needed the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are. The medicine and some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got up a while ago and went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's also feeling sick and went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been knocking on the door,\Nbut the guy inside won't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir? Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it came from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I have your attention, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a passenger who has fallen ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there is a doctor or nurse on board,\Nplease report to your nearest flight attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Megure from the MPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there really a sick person aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone {\i1}died{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's in the toilet in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did he wander off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? If it isn't Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Off on vacation during the school break?{vs.Off on vacation during the long weekend?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard that somebody {\i1}died{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Just leave everything to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody has disturbed the scene, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, some strange boy did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was most likely\Nsuffocation by damage to the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is a pointed object, similar to an ice pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim may have already been unconscious from inhaling some kind of chemical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough information for that yet.{pre-gonbe-edit:That's what I don't know yet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer is still in this big tin can\Nthat's flying above the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let that person get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was the first page in his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kudō, detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This was Shin'ichi's first case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kudō? Are you Yūsaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're his son, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the spitting image of your dad in the old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since\Nyou were in the sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But man, you've grown so tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you've got no business here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're still in high school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just meddle with a crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Could you borrow a camera from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to take pictures of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you need pictures,\Nthat boy already took some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About sixty, I believe. I borrowed the camera from a passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us to keep an eye on his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't do anything suspicious, like trying to hide something or wipe something off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you move the body, you'll destroy the stiffening of the muscles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making it harder to determine\Nthe estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the livor mortis and the\Nfact that his chin was already stiffening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd say he's been dead for an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three things that struck me as being just plain odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, even though there were spots of\Nblood on the wall where the body was leaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there wasn't any blood on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secondly, there's a strange scratch at\Nthe lower right of the fatal wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And last but not least, the inside of his\Ntrousers' left pocket was soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though his hands were completely dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if you shove a wet hand into your pocket, it wouldn't get that wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that somebody\Nmust've soaked it for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Argh! Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to leave this to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but could you get the man sleeping in the seat next to mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, 'detective'?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just a regular high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let me get near the body otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've told me where you were going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried sick about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were sleeping so peacefully with that dopey look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by dopey look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murder case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was most likely\Nsuffocation by damage to the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is a pointed object, similar to an ice pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the livor mortis and rigor mortis, he died one or two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? There's an empty bottle and a handkerchief in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the killer soaked the handkerchief in something like chloroform, carried it around in a bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:07.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and knocked the victim out with it before killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We'd like to store the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I have a plastic bag or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that everything you just said has been exactly the same as what that boy said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'That boy'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look. The one over there with the black pullover.{sweater in en_US, jumper in en_GB, we decided to use pullover to avoid en_US AND any confusement}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His dad's a mystery writer who used to help me whenever I couldn't figure out a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he was still little, his dad used to bring him along to crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never would've thought he'd pick up detection skills like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An amateur's still an amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:03.88,Dialogue,,2,2,0,,He's just a teenager who got big ideas from\Nreading too many mysteries and medical books!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, let's look for potential witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with four suspects here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only four people, apart from the victim, went to the toilet at the key time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My seat's at the very end of the row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had my eyes open the whole night, and\Nnobody went to the smoking area behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had your eyes open?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were awake all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I couldn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you fall asleep the\Nmoment you got on the plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:45.75,Dialogue,,2,2,0,,Oh, boy! Falling asleep early and then waking up in the middle of the night, just like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:53.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You really expected me to fall asleep with you right next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not that mature yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then could you identify\Nthose four people for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the four people were...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the woman next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the man sitting across the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the foreigner in the seat in front is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all seated close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did this happen to Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those negatives could be a motive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Negatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him showing them off to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed he'd earn big money by selling them to some newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he didn't have any on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the murderer must be someone who was aware of those negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anybody in our business would've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He offered to sell them to plenty of newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ōtaka was stabbed in the back of the head, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the killer must've been a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are just photographers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a bit off base to suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it could've been done by anyone with an anaesthetic weapon and basic medical knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, even a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for now, let's hear you all\Nout about your trips to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the toilet because I wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm certain that Kazuhiro was still there when I got back to my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, I asked the stewardess to bring me some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why I still remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He still seemed to be asleep, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw that from down the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It indeed looked as if she was asking for some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the toilet right after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I was there for about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Down the aisle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't your seat across from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking around since I don't like sitting for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when did the victim leave his seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I brought her the medicine\Nand water, he had already left his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm fairly certain that I got back in less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the bathroom about twenty\Nminutes after Tsugumi got her medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:19:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to see how Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was doing\Nbecause he had been away for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when I knocked on this door and asked wheter he was doing fine, he knocked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know\Nwhich one he was in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked all the other ones\Nand they were all unoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.52,Signs,,0,0,24,,When did you go to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember when I did, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says he doesn't remember when he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That foreigner uses a really strong cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! How many more useless questions will you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever has the murder weapon must be the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster to just perform a body check on those four and check their luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since I never went to the toilet and was asleep the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also left your seat, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your seat's right behind the victim's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:18.19,Dialogue,,2,2,0,,Remember how I said the victim was still\Nasleep in his seat before I went to the toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear that he wasn't there at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's just crazy talk, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only you and the other three went to the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he testified!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, I {\i1}was{\i0}\Ndistracted for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I must ask all five of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to get bodychecked in the lavatory and have your baggage searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't find a weapon on them or in their bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, nobody had anything\Nsimilar to an ice pick on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have also searched all\Npossible spots on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure they were the only ones who went to the lavatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the murder weapon couldn't be found, then that must mean
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the murderer is probably still carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that must be the culprit's trump card.{very probably not a thought, though who knows...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And I'll find that trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before this iron bird rests its wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Search them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:22:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want us to do a full search of the five suspects and their belongings once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we can't find the\Nweapon on board the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the murderer might still be\Ncarrying it, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First up, Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, purse{en_gb;was wallet}, handkerchief,\Nmakeup kit, tissues, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a pair of sunglasses, camera,\Nnotebook, and a ballpoint pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of this could be a potential murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that ballpoint pen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you look inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up is Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief,\Nknit hat, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,camera, makeup kit, sewing kit and some medicine for airsickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only edged tools here are the small\Nscissors and needle in the sewing kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like a far stretch to think someone could kill with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up is Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, boarding pass, wallet, handkerchief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,electric razor, towel and some shaving cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Next up is Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us check your belongings, just in case.{it's probably either 'Let us...' or 'Well, let's...'<GonbeFAN> might be 'Will I' too\N<GonbeFAN> probably 'Let us' though\N<GonbeFAN> or maybe 'We'll' ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it appears you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:38.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:43.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The cologne is the most strong around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:45.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe he has none on his wrists.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief, boarding pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,towel, newspaper, two paperback books, glasses case, sewing kit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:23:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a checkbook from the\NAmerican National Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this checkbook...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr Edward, I'd like to ask you a few questions\Nabout the checkbook in your briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's for my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.01,0:24:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was to buy some art object\Nat the auction in Japan.{art or foreign object? probably art, though}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But nothing caught my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He intended to buy an art\Nobject at an auction in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he couldn't find anything to his interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.86,0:24:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the last one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.82,0:24:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, wallet, handkerchief, camera, some negatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wristwatch, cigarettes, lighter, boarding pass and medicine for airsickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot of medicine you've got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I easily get airsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.51,0:24:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chizuru and Tsugumi lent me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.63,0:24:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:24:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mind if I look at those negatives real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:24:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in these photographs...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.06,0:25:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the American senator Dickson{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.03,0:25:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's with a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.03,0:25:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's enough, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds just like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just like his? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.75,0:25:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here they are in your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.33,0:25:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.96,0:25:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-These are {\i1}my{\i0} negatives!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.71,0:25:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at that hotel with Ōtaka, taking the same pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ōtaka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.39,0:25:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ōtaka's were better than mine.\NMine weren't so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.10,0:25:45.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was gonna try sell 'em anyway to some newspaper office in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.06,0:25:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you want to blame the murder\Non me, then go find the weapon first!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.32,0:25:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. I'll be happy\Nto talk after the body check.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.45,0:25:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, I'd like everyone to enter\Nthe toilet, one at a time, as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.20,0:26:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stewardess will be checking the woman,\Nwhile the men will be checked by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.62,0:26:10.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So this is Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.42,0:26:13.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}According to the seat numbers on the boarding passes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:17.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was behind him,\Nand in front of him sat Edward{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.51,0:26:21.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Amano{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} sat to his right, and next to her was Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:24.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And across the aisle to his left sat Ukai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.98,0:26:34.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a fragment of a film negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:36.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's it doing in the seat\Nnext to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.45,0:26:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.45,0:26:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just finished the body check.{Viz: The body check's finished, but they haven't found a weapon!}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like nobody had a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.12,0:26:49.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means the only place left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.62,0:26:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see now? We didn't have any weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.09,0:26:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to strip buck naked {\i1}twice{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:27:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What do we do, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.10,0:27:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've searched every possible place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.18,0:27:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's still one more place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.02,0:27:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a place we haven't searched yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The luggage of the victim, Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.70,0:27:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one belongs to Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.29,0:27:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.08,0:27:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one behind that black bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.09,0:27:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.46,0:27:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something unusual he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.05,0:27:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something unusual...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.22,0:27:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A week ago, he forgot his bag in the studio, and somebody tore it to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.73,0:27:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he had to buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.94,0:28:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a new one for this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody thought the\Nnegatives might've been inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passport, camera, film, a pair of\Nsunglasses, three packs of cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wallet, towel, two magazines,\Nboarding pass, and wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.21,0:28:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like this looks like\Nthe murder weapon to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.05,0:28:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.09,0:28:25.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.68,0:28:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.18,0:28:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Kazuhiro Ōtaka'.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.35,0:28:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who won the {\i1}Nichiuri Shimbun{\i0} Photo Awards three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.73,0:28:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.69,0:28:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same Kazuhiro Ōtaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.74,0:28:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.03,0:28:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.36,0:28:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That photograph of a mother caught in a fire handing her baby to a fireman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.17,0:28:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.08,0:28:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that currently matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are we cleared of the charges now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.96,0:29:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or not? Well, which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.42,0:29:06.93,Dialogue,,2,2,0,,B-But you people were the only ones who went\Nto the toilet around the time of the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.93,0:29:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...according to this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.56,0:29:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet the young detective simply fell asleep and missed a couple of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.36,0:29:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems like you've read lots of books and did lots of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.45,0:29:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not some fictional story.{BuriBot, j-ball shousetsu 3! (J-Ball) 小説 [しょうせつ] /(n,adj-no) novel/(short) story/(P)/}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.91,0:29:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children should behave and just go back to their seat, and take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.41,0:29:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.87,0:29:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna stand up to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:37.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:40.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can't find the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.71,0:29:43.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And their stories just don't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.26,0:29:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's about time to confess already?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.64,0:29:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.43,0:29:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the murderer, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.85,0:29:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's pretty obvious that you're\Nthe only one among us who's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When this lady asked for some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.69,0:30:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You claimed you were in your\Nseat back then, but that's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.16,0:30:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.24,0:30:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's not nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.24,0:30:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that... back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.04,0:30:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That stewardess...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.66,0:30:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also must've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or so he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.21,0:30:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.13,0:30:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.63,0:30:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gentleman was wandering\Naround the cabin, so I stopped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.68,0:30:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then complained about someone who\Nwas smoking in the non-smoking section.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.06,0:30:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was this person in his seat back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.15,0:30:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.57,0:30:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.95,0:30:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.16,0:30:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the one who brought the medicine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.91,0:30:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.41,0:30:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You saw me asleep in my seat, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.92,0:31:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.46,0:31:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.80,0:31:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.55,0:31:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that when you brought the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.72,0:31:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes, you're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.89,0:31:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.23,0:31:21.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.52,0:31:23.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.77,0:31:25.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:29.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All testimonies except the killer's...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:32.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The negative fragement in the seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.24,0:31:35.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The unusual bloodstain in the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.74,0:31:38.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And why the victim's pockets were wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:40.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It all fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.17,0:31:42.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.21,0:31:45.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why did we not find the weapon on the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.30,0:31:48.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.59,0:31:50.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That it couldn't be thrown away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.47,0:31:52.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something that'd lead us\Nimmediately to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.39,0:31:57.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.52,0:31:59.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Back then that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.35,0:32:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.19,0:32:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure is looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.94,0:32:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to ask you wheter or not you remember anyone else who went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.86,0:32:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, more importantly, Ran, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.95,0:32:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...in high school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.36,0:32:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.24,0:32:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, lemme ask you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.25,0:32:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wh-Wha-Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.08,0:32:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer already!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.71,0:32:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing for me too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.92,0:32:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.21,0:32:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of them are like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.18,0:32:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.22,0:32:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.47,0:32:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just what do you mean by 'I see'?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.60,0:32:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.77,0:32:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trump card that the killer used to finish off the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.82,0:32:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.99,0:32:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one of you who has\Nmade any suspicious moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.32,0:32:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is you, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.91,0:32:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.58,0:33:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.41,0:33:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is not the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.96,0:33:12.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man never went near the crime scene,\Nso there's a 0% chance that he's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.76,0:33:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.80,0:33:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.55,0:33:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you I wasn't involved with any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.06,0:33:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.02,0:33:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} involved in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.69,0:33:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.36,0:33:29.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were being used by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.03,0:33:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By one of those four people who isn't telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.32,0:33:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.78,0:33:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.74,0:33:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who claims to have gone to the toilet to check on the victim, knocked on the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that then someone knocked back was Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.12,0:33:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She lied?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.71,0:33:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.29,0:33:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.00,0:33:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.42,0:33:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really was someone inside the toilet room...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.01,0:33:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together with a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.97,0:34:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that was you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.18,0:34:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.10,0:34:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While looking for the negatives he put his hand inside Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.31,0:34:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and realised that some of the cologne from his wrists got on the victim's trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.49,0:34:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he quickly washed the cologne off his hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.49,0:34:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wiped that distinctive scent out of the pocket with a wet handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him not having any cologne on his wrists is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.13,0:34:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really classify as proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.42,0:34:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the questioning would have to be done in English.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.26,0:34:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he can actually speak Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.01,0:34:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.72,0:34:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.23,0:34:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.81,0:34:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.98,0:34:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...in Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.15,0:34:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.65,0:34:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to buy those negatives with that National Bank check.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.82,0:35:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.16,0:35:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.91,0:35:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senator Dickson, the man in those\Nscandalous photos, requested me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.37,0:35:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who killed Ōtaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.12,0:35:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.21,0:35:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when he entered the toilet, Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was already a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.18,0:35:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.93,0:35:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I heard that he went to the toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.31,0:35:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I realised that it was my opportunity to make a deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.06,0:35:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I got no reply after knocking on the door, I forced myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there he was... Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.45,0:35:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't get my hands on the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.91,0:35:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the one who knocked back were...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.41,0:35:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.33,0:35:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just playing along with the kid's guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.63,0:35:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.46,0:35:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.17,0:36:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was blood on the toilet's wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.76,0:36:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't any on the victim's back\Neven though that he was leaning there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.22,0:36:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That indicates that someone else\Nmust've moved the body later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.69,0:36:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who found the body without notifying anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.02,0:36:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only reason I could think of to move the body would be to look for the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.24,0:36:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unable to find it, he searched inside the victim's pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.54,0:36:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only person who would do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.29,0:36:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,must have been someone who couldn't see what the victim was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.54,0:36:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person would be Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.84,0:36:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.59,0:36:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who's the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.30,0:36:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have now ruled out Edward{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and the\None who knocked on the door, Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.80,0:36:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and\NAmano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are the only suspects left.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.10,0:36:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's an important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.23,0:36:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked a\Nstewardess for some medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.02,0:37:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there was nobody sitting in Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nseat — the one behind the victim's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.65,0:37:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Ukai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.49,0:37:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.16,0:37:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I kept telling you that I was asleep in my seat the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.49,0:37:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nsleeping in his seat the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.42,0:37:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the killer put a knit hat and an eye mask on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.88,0:37:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.01,0:37:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, doesn't that match...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.97,0:37:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it matches what\NŌtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wore while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.68,0:37:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After killing Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, instead of returning to their own seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.39,0:37:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the killer sat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} while being\Ndressed like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and called the stewardess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.69,0:37:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way it'd seem like Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still alive at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.61,0:37:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.20,0:37:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.82,0:37:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.82,0:37:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and used Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to create a fake alibi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.92,0:38:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi Amano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.72,0:38:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.39,0:38:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.39,0:38:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't blame the stewardess\Nfor her mistake, because it was so dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.81,0:38:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and most of his face was covered up.{*UTB: & the only part of his not covered by the blanket, was the nose up...Viz: and she couldn't see much of the person under the blanket.UTB seems more literal, but is weirdly worded, please reTL}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.90,0:38:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went back to her own seat when the stewardess was getting the medicine,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.15,0:38:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and woke up Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by coughing loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.50,0:38:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All to make her notice that Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't in his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.83,0:38:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus making Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and the stewardess think that Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.05,0:38:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-In that case, the empty seat I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.34,0:38:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've seen the empty seat behind Sazanuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.35,0:38:58.19,Dialogue,,3,3,0,,But she wouldn't be able to pull off that trick if the\Nseat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was to be occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.19,0:39:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she ordered an extra ticket without\Ncancelling it, the seat {\i1}would{\i0} remain empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:09.61,Dialogue,,5,5,0,,If she gave Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sleeping pills instead\Nof airsick pills, then he wouldn't wake up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.24,0:39:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a knit hat in her luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.87,0:39:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she was aware of Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s habit of wearing an eye mask when sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.13,0:39:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if the stewardess noticed Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wasn't sitting next to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.88,0:39:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that can easily be camouflaged by putting a blanket over your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The negatives were cut to pieces with the sewing kit's scissors and flushed down the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.73,0:39:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All to make it look like that the killer was after the negatives
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.06,0:39:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to draw away attention from her and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.03,0:39:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a piece of the negative on the seat next to Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.15,0:39:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which must've stuck to her\Nclothes and fell down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.74,0:39:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.87,0:39:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.58,0:39:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.20,0:40:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She waited until Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.17,0:40:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that she wanted to talk and told him to wait in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.34,0:40:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She then took her drugged handkerchief in\Na bottle and weapon, and went to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.80,0:40:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after opening the door, she pressed the handkerchief into his face to knock him out,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.39,0:40:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stabbed him in the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.27,0:40:22.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now she had to cut up and flush away the negatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.39,0:40:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lock the door from the outside, and set up her trick so that it seems Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still was alive
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.82,0:40:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when she returned from the toilet.\NHer alibi was now established.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.41,0:40:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if someone going to the toilet saw her leaving the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that she left the door unlocked during the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.67,0:40:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even if someone wanted to use the toilet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.92,0:40:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she could easily keep the door closed because of it being so narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.39,0:40:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person outside would realise that it's occupied and just go to another toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.18,0:41:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.02,0:41:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to accuse Tsugumi then you better show us some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.52,0:41:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the weapon and proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.65,0:41:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, she still has it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.78,0:41:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you blabbering about? You forgot that she went through two body checks?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.41,0:41:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that can bypass a search.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.91,0:41:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also can get past metal detectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.42,0:41:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only women have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.29,0:41:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Only women have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.30,0:41:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if something that convenient exists, you silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.97,0:41:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me, Tsugumi, that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.18,0:41:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I'm talking about, Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.52,0:41:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the metal wire in the right\Nside of the bra you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.94,0:41:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for a woman to\Nkill someone with such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.53,0:41:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, if you sharpen one edge and stab the back of the neck with full power,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.20,0:42:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and penetrate about 5 to 6 centimetres, it'll reach the cervical cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.25,0:42:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.00,0:42:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a peculiar scratch mark left near the fatal injury on his neck. That's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.67,0:42:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been left there when the other end of the wire scratched the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.34,0:42:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't get rid of the weapon because if it'd be discovered at the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.35,0:42:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'd figure out that the woman with\Na missing wire in her bra would be the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.02,0:42:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! Let's just have her go\Nthrough one more body check.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.99,0:42:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, Saginuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.41,0:42:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because then they'd find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.12,0:42:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.62,0:42:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.96,0:42:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed Kazuhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.09,0:42:57.59,Dialogue,,3,3,0,,Because of the photo that made him win the\N{\i1}Nichiuri Shimbun{\i0} Photo Award three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.22,0:43:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? Wasn't that photo what brought you two together?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.18,0:43:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. He caught my interest because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.98,0:43:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was amazed that someone was able to capture the horror of the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.65,0:43:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that took my brother's life, on film.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.74,0:43:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.86,0:43:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the only photo he took.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.33,0:43:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found dozens of photos in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.41,0:43:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some from when the smoke started to rise from the flat building,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.92,0:43:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even panoramic shots from before the fire even started!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.71,0:43:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did Ōtaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.47,0:43:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...start that fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.89,0:43:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! He even boasted about it when I confronted him with the photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.93,0:43:51.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You don't wait for perfect\Nmoments. You {\i1}make{\i0} them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.23,0:43:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.11,0:44:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.32,0:44:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.16,0:44:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was confident in where I hid the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.79,0:44:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You raised your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.66,0:44:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were about to get his bag from the luggage rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.50,0:44:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your right arm stopped and then you used your left arm instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.26,0:44:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gave you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.01,0:44:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sharpened edge of the wire must've\Npricked you, which is what made you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.93,0:44:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-From that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.43,0:44:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From {\i1}just{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.52,0:44:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has long been an axiom of mine that the little things are infinitely the most important.{IMPORTANT - he might possibly not be quoting Holmes word-for-word}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.03,0:44:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That little gesture you made just struck me as odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.20,0:44:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her arm... Did you notice it, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.42,0:44:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.01,0:45:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.34,0:45:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to LA?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.64,0:45:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to pick up a Japanese criminal who's on the international list from the LAPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.64,0:45:10.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.10,0:45:12.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.98,0:45:15.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he asked me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.70,0:46:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.45,0:46:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Could you show me your bra?'
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.74,0:46:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'There's a wire in it, isn't there?'
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.54,0:46:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who asks a woman such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.00,0:46:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that's\Nsexual harassment, Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.88,0:47:01.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.21,0:47:03.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me Ran's dreaming about {\i1}that{\i0} case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.92,0:47:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.97,0:47:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That creep {\i1}did{\i0} try something, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.39,0:47:12.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.39,0:47:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's she dreaming about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.18,0:47:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dreamt about stuffing myself with eel on rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.73,0:47:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, we're about to land. Please return to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.94,0:47:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! How can I stay calm when my daughter's virtue is endangered!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.07,0:47:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.45,0:47:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.45,0:47:31.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}sekuhara
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta mean a dessert stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.57,0:47:33.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}betsubara
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.51,0:47:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.40,0:47:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.18,0:47:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.66,0:47:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The less I understand of it, the more it goes wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.40,0:48:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My uncontrollable curiosity!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.52,0:48:08.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,The Secret of the Moon, Star and Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.52,0:48:08.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.52,0:48:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: 'The Secret of the Moon, Star and Sun (Part I)'.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.53,0:48:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: ¥1 coin!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.49,0:48:19.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.49,0:48:15.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode is on the 11th of October!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.12,0:48:19.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran, when're you gonna\Ndream about me again?
